OL,6,FThey were heading to Venice, where
OL,7,Fthey would meet up with their ship
OL,8,Fbefore touring the Mediterranean.
OL,10,FWhilst in the air, they were told that
OL,11,Ftheir luggage hadn't made it due to
OL,12,Fthe fault, and since then, they say
OL,13,Fthey have had no clear updates from
OL,14,FBritish Airways.
OL,16,FSteve told ITV Meridian it was a
OL,17,Fstressful start to their holiday. He
OL,18,Fsaid: "Just before we landed in Marco
OL,19,FPolo airport in Venice, the captain
OL,20,Fcame on and said he had an
OL,21,Fannouncement.
