OL,6,F"It was bad news, and he said the
OL,7,Faircraft had left without luggage.
OL,9,F"He'd been told to leave Heathrow
OL,10,Fwithout luggage, but he was hoping
OL,11,Fthat the luggage would be on the
OL,12,Faircraft that would be following later
OL,13,Fin the evening.
OL,15,F"We've got AirTags on our luggage, and
OL,16,Fwe could see that the AirTags were
OL,17,Fstill sitting in Heathrow Airport."
OL,19,FWatch: Steve tells ITV Meridian about
OL,20,Fthe experience with BA.
