OL,6,FThe tracking tags show that Steve's
OL,7,Fluggage did eventually make it to
OL,8,FVenice, but not in time for the cruise.
OL,10,FThey're currently in Greece and have
OL,11,Fhad to buy new clothes, which Stephen
OL,12,Fsaid has been covered by their
OL,13,Finsurance.
OL,15,FNow the couple are hoping their
OL,16,Fluggage can be returned to Heathrow so
OL,17,Fthey can collect it when they return.
