OL,6,F"It's just been a shame really", Steve
OL,7,Fsaid. "It has made it a bit difficult,
OL,8,Fa bit stressful, a bit anxious not
OL,9,Fhaving it... I mean, we're on a
OL,10,Fbeautiful cruise ship, and we can't
OL,11,Fdress up at night.
OL,13,F"Everything is fine with BA if
OL,14,Feverything goes fine on the flight. -
OL,15,Fthe people who work on the aircraft
OL,16,Fare lovely people.
