OL,6,F"But if anything goes wrong, that is
OL,7,Fwhen you have the issues. You just
OL,8,Fcan't get any help, no communication -
OL,9,Fyou don't know where you are - and if
OL,10,Fit wasn't for the fact we had air tags
OL,11,Fin our luggage we just would not know
OL,12,Fwhere the luggage was."
OL,14,FIn a statement, a British Airways
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "We apologised to
OL,16,Fthose customers who were unable to
OL,17,Ftravel with their luggage due to a
OL,18,Ftemporary technical fault that was
OL,19,Foutside our control.
